  <entry>
    <id>tag:github.com,2008:Grit::Commit/fc8d777e41b2dd1128671021c220cb217cffced1</id>
    <link type="text/html" rel="alternate" href="https://github.com/shurik179/TQFTbook/commit/fc8d777e41b2dd1128671021c220cb217cffced1"/>
    <title>
        Add venv requirements files + README Setup section
    </title>
    <updated>2026-06-17T14:20:47Z</updated>
    <media:thumbnail height="30" width="30" url="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/12883611?s=30&amp;v=4"/>
    <author>
      <name>shurik179</name>
      <uri>https://github.com/shurik179</uri>
    </author>
    <content type="html">
      &lt;pre style=&#39;white-space:pre-wrap;width:81ex&#39;&gt;Add venv requirements files + README Setup section

Pin both venvs (requirements-tex.txt / requirements-web.txt, generated from the
working venvs with local-path lines normalized) and document how to recreate
them from a fresh clone, including re-applying the Gerby-renderer patches.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 &amp;lt;noreply@anthropic.com&amp;gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
    </content>
  </entry>
